18. What is meaning of 'STATISTTICS' ?

=> ✅ Whatever input optimizer is collect that called 'STATISTTICS'. These input are help optimizer to choose a best execution plan for SQL query. 

   📌 SENARIO :- Suppose, on 'EMP' table 12AM stat gather has done. Means, optimizer knows how many records like, rows, columns, indexes etc has in 'EMP' table (example- 10k). 

   📌 Now, After 12AM (12am to 7am) somebody inserted bulk records. Suppose 10k more records added now and in between indexes also drop by someone. 

   📌 Now, When stat gather has done at 12AM after that all the activities that are happend optimizer doesn't know about that. 
   So, in that senario when optimizer give plan it's very high to that plan will not be proper and bad plan. And this plan will be harmfull for queries.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

