21. Exclusive Lock :

=>	👉 Exclusive lock ka matlab hota hai resource par full control
Dusra user us data ko modify nahi kar sakta.

	Session 1:

	UPDATE emp SET salary = 9000 WHERE emp_id = 101;


	Session 2:

	UPDATE emp SET salary = 10000 WHERE emp_id = 101;


	👉 Session 2 wait karega jab tak Session 1 commit/rollback nahi karta.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

22. Deadlock :

=>	👉 Deadlock tab hota hai jab do ya zyada sessions ek dusre ka lock hold kar lete hain aur wait karte rehte hain.

	Session 1:
UPDATE emp SET salary = 5000 WHERE emp_id = 101;

Session 2:
UPDATE emp SET salary = 6000 WHERE emp_id = 102;


Ab:

Session 1 tries:

UPDATE emp SET salary = 7000 WHERE emp_id = 102;


Session 2 tries:

UPDATE emp SET salary = 8000 WHERE emp_id = 101;


👉 Result:

Session 1 → Session 2 ka lock wait karega

Session 2 → Session 1 ka lock wait karega

💥 Deadlock ho gaya
